accessibility.text: Rich dives and loves the experience. He felt like he hasnt relaxed in so long. He feels happy that he didnt let his fears overpower his wish.
While he learns diving he finds the diving instructor charming and feels special about her.
Julia invites all of them to the Tamatina festival.
John and Ahmed get really excited and are ready to alter the plans but they don't wanna mess up with Rich's plans.
Rich says        No, Work                  Yes, Fun
